sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte CalendarView)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant PA as PlanAccess
    participant R as Repository (Git)

    Note over C,R: Single cell copy-paste

    C->>C: Click day text cell → select cell
    C->>C: Ctrl+C → copy selected DayFocus data to clipboard
    C->>C: Click target day text cell → select target
    C->>C: Ctrl+V → paste

    C->>A: SaveDayFocus({targetDate, source.themeIds, source.text, target.notes, source.okrIds, source.tags})
    A->>PM: SaveDayFocus(access.DayFocus)
    PM->>PA: SaveDayFocus(day)
    PA->>PA: GetYearFocus(year) [read existing]
    PA->>PA: Upsert entry, preserving target notes
    PA->>PA: WriteJSON(calendar/{year}.json)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PA-->>PM: nil
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: Multi-cell range copy-paste (clamped to month)

    C->>C: Click day 1 text cell → select anchor
    C->>C: Shift+Click day 3 text cell → extend selection (within same month)
    C->>C: Ctrl+C → copy 3 DayFocus entries to clipboard
    C->>C: Click target day text cell (e.g. day 30)
    C->>C: Ctrl+V → paste range starting at target

    loop For each source day offset (0, 1, 2)
        C->>C: Compute target date = target + offset
        alt Target date within same month
            C->>A: SaveDayFocus({targetDate, source[offset].themeIds, source[offset].text, existing.notes, ...})
            A->>PM: SaveDayFocus(access.DayFocus)
            PM->>PA: SaveDayFocus(day)
            PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
            PA-->>PM: nil
            PM-->>A: nil
            A-->>C: nil
        else Target date exceeds month boundary
            C->>C: Skip — paste clamped to month
        end
    end

    Note over C,R: Selection management
    C->>C: Escape key → clear all selection
    C->>C: Click outside grid → clear all selection
    C->>C: Shift+Click across months → treated as single click (no range)
